   [$ (^Attorney.^) $] Did not (^Barker^) bring (^Rodolph^) to you
at nine of the Clock at Night? Did he not leave
with you Instructions in (^French^) ?
   [$ (^Duke.^) $] I confess it.

   [$Then was read (^Barker^) to the 16th.$]

   [$ (^Attorney.^) $] (^Rodolph^) came also the second time
to the Duke; after he was come from the Duke,
he said to (^Barker^) , That the Duke and he were
<P 106C1>
agreed of his Journey, and that the Duke pray'd
