(^Walloons^) should have landed, (^&c.^)
   Then was read the Bishop of (^Rosse's^) to the 12
and 13, to the same effect.

   Then Mr. Sollicitor recited again the Effect of
the Letters, and the said Confessions of (^Rosse^) and
