   [$ (^Duke.^) $] I read not that Letter, but of another
Matter, and you bring but one Witness to prove it.
   [$ (^Sollic.^) $] There be two Witnesses, (^Barker^) and the
Bishop of (^Rosse^) , severally examined, who agreed
directly, expressing it. And (^Bayly^) also wrote the
